#: ../../source/developer_guide/extending_lmcache/native_connectors.rst:226
msgid ""
"This gives you ``batch_get``, ``batch_set``, ``batch_exists`` (async), "
"and their synchronous variants, all with automatic eventfd-driven "
"completion handling."
